<chapter xml:id="chapter_16" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"><title>Recurrence Relations</title>
<introduction>
<p>The goal of this chapter is to discuss recurrence relations. Recurrence relations are a recursive framework essential in computer science. We will concentrate on methods of solving recurrence relations, including an introduction to generating
functions.
